description: The landmark EU-UK deal is on its way to becoming law provisionally on 1 January.
title: Brexit: EU ambassadors approve EU-UK trade deal
title_page: Brexit: EU ambassadors approve EU-UK trade deal - BBC News
maintext: They have had three days to analyse the details of the EU-UK Trade and Co-operation Agreement, since its publication. But most of the 1,246-page document had already been seen by member states in previous weeks.
